Error Junction - location of identified QC issues to be investigated point
Island Junction - location where closed island segment begins and terminates at the same point point
Mean Water Junction - location where mean high water level changes along the coastline (WACO meets WACO) point
Network Flow Junction - intersection of network linear flow (skeleton / spine) with a delimiter point
Provincial Limit Junction - intersection of Provincial Limit with hydro feature (WARV*50etc.) point
River Junction - intersection of 3 or more WARV5* WARVSP5* or WADI5*
Skeleton Junction - intersection of 3 or more skeleton / spine linear elements point
Shoreline Junction - intersection of network linear flow feature and shoreline elements point
Source Junction - location of the start or origin of a network linear flow point
Water Boundary Junction - location where delimiter and water boundary entities intersect point
